    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this wonderful find! This car is in good condition and has clearly been well-loved, offering a smooth, dependable driving experience that you can count on. The exterior still shines beautifully with only minor, everyday wear, and the interior is clean and comfortable. It\u2019s a fantastic, reliable vehicle that\u2019s ready for its next adventure with you!",
